skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen to daily updates from your favorite Chicago source. You can just say "Alexa, what's my flash briefing". You can say "Alexa, stop" to exit anytime.
What is up, what is new, get it all here.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
